OL,6,FThe artwork seized by Gwent Police
OL,7,Finclude Grappling Hook, a large
OL,8,Fcrucifix with hooks created in 2017
OL,9,Fand estimated to be worth up to
OL,10,F#210,000; a satirical portrait of the
OL,11,Flate Queen called Monkey Queen,
OL,12,Festimated to be worth around #13,000;
OL,13,Fand the Watchtower Swing portrait.
OL,15,FAs well as the artwork, Gwent Police
OL,16,Fsay the group used the funds from
OL,17,Ftheir drug sales to buy designer
OL,18,Fitems, a caravan, quad bikes and jet
OL,19,Fskis with an estimated value of
OL,20,F#48,400.
