OL,6,FThe group of men and women from Ebbw
OL,7,FVale, Blaenau Gwent, appeared before
OL,8,FNewport Crown Court to be sentenced
OL,9,Ffor their roles in the part in the
OL,10,Fimportation, production and supply of
OL,11,Fcannabis on Friday, 11 October.
OL,13,FChristopher Scrivens, 37, was jailed
OL,14,Ffor three years after pleading guilty
OL,15,Fto the importation of and conspiracy
OL,16,Fto supply cannabis.
