OL,3,CDrug-dealing group bought Banksy
OL,4,Cartwork with money from cannabis sales
OL,6,FSix others were sentenced for a range
OL,7,Fof offences which include being
OL,8,Fconcerned in the production of a class
OL,9,FB drug, conspiracy to supply a class B
OL,10,Fdrug and possession of criminal
OL,11,Fproperty.
OL,13,FThey were handed community orders and
OL,14,Fwill have to complete unpaid work,
OL,15,Fwhile an eighth defendant, Rebecca
OL,16,FMills, will be sentenced at a later
OL,17,Fdate.
OL,19,FThe Banksy artwork is due to be part
OL,20,Fof a Proceeds of Crime Act process in
OL,21,Fthe coming months.
