OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Mike
OL,7,FPreston, of Gwent Police, said: "This
OL,8,Fis a particularly complex case, where
OL,9,Fthe defendants have attempted to hide
OL,10,Fthe proceeds of their crimes in
OL,11,Fextravagant items of clothing,
OL,12,Fvehicles, and artwork.
OL,14,F"I'd like to thank all the officers
OL,15,Fand staff within Gwent Police for
OL,16,Ftheir hard work to bring these
OL,17,Fdefendants before the courts and
OL,18,Fensure thousands of pounds of criminal
OL,19,Fassets have been seized.
