OL,6,F"Taking away the assets that criminals
OL,7,Fhave purchased through crime sends the
OL,8,Fmessage that crime does not pay.
OL,10,F"Drug dealers cause misery to our
OL,11,Fcommunities; they have no
OL,12,Fconsideration for the distress and
OL,13,Ffear they cause, and we will continue
OL,14,Fto target anyone intent on causing our
OL,15,Fneighbourhoods harm."
